OL,3,CCovid Inquiry: Matt Hancock says PPE
OL,4,Cwas within hours from running out
OL,6,FHospitals in England were within
OL,7,F"hours" of running out of personal
OL,8,Fprotective equipment (PPE) during the
OL,9,Fearly months of Covid , Matt Hancock
OL,10,Fhas revealed.
OL,12,FThe former Tory health secretary told
OL,13,Fthe Covid inquiry on Thursday that
OL,14,Fsome PPE was in very short supply
OL,15,Fduring the first wave of the pandemic
OL,16,Fin 2020.
