OL,6,F"We came extremely close. We came
OL,7,Fwithin small numbers of items on a
OL,8,Fregular basis during April and May
OL,9,F2020 ` by the second wave, we were in
OL,10,Fbetter shape."
OL,12,FAsked about if there was no more stock
OL,13,Fof gowns in April 2020, he explained:
OL,14,F"Gowns I think at one point we got to
OL,15,Fwithin six or seven hours of running
OL,16,Fout.
OL,18,F"We were working incredibly hard to
OL,19,Fmake sure that we didn't (run out). We
OL,20,Fnearly did."
